text_raw:
2. The percentage rate shall, in lieu of the percentage rate specified in 
subsection (4)(a) of section 3F of the Insurance Act 1964 (No. 18 of 1964), be 
one per cent of the assessable amount. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

24 October, 2023. 

MICHAEL MCGRATH, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 27th October, 2023.
